ALB-Ingress-ContextPath-Based-Routing
Review Nginx App1, App2 & App3 Deployment & Service

 Create ALB Ingress Context path based Routing Kubernetes manifest
04-ALB-Ingress-ContextPath-Based-Routing.yml

 Deploy all manifests and test
 # Deploy Kubernetes manifests
kubectl apply -f kube-manifests/
